reviewText: I decided to purchase this in VHS format because I still like to use videos and see nothing wrong with this style of viewing.  The Grand children love it and can enjoy this video anytime they choose. It views very well and.  I think if you're trying to build a collection for the young ones, this is a good way to go.
I bought this used and it works great and it was in good shape. There is more then just one episode on it.
